    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/82891905a75f5f762f6a6b495b7fb7d4.poster.avif?t=1653020164\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/82891905a75f5f762f6a6b495b7fb7d4.webm?t=1653020164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/82891905a75f5f762f6a6b495b7fb7d4.mp4?t=1653020164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Grid Miner is a real-time strategy puzzle game where you mine asteroids to gather resources and expand your space station. Unlock new tools and utilities as you progress through levels. Maintain your quotas and learn more about your employer and coworkers at Hypergo Industries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/1e748d57711c13eed63d9e5afe77368e.poster.avif?t=1653020164\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/1e748d57711c13eed63d9e5afe77368e.webm?t=1653020164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/1e748d57711c13eed63d9e5afe77368e.mp4?t=1653020164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>18 unique buildings like power plants, asteroid crushers, tractor beams and more!<br></li><li>15 levels to test your skills<br></li><li>Rich backstory about Hypergo Industries and its employees<br></li><li>Unlock rewards and new buildings as you progress through levels<br></li><li>Relaxing original soundtrack<br></li><li>4 different color pallets</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/23b4ad5a5e19aab23cfca4edc5f86851.poster.avif?t=1653020164\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/23b4ad5a5e19aab23cfca4edc5f86851.webm?t=1653020164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768300/extras/23b4ad5a5e19aab23cfca4edc5f86851.mp4?t=1653020164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
